{"tid":1492872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"喂 無野？我有野啊喂！喂！內地女子偷拍記者 拒出示記者證 警員護送下離開","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T06:36:41.000Z","uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"beb894014bd14892e7386456549abc6cdce4077a","tid":1492872,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）在今日警方例行記者會上，有一名操普通話的女子以手機拍攝在席記者，並將照片上載至微信，惟該名女子並沒有配戴記者證。記者會結束後，《蘋果日報》記者要求該女子出示記者證，及解釋拍攝在席記者的原因。該女子及後離席，向在場的公共關係科警員求助。她拒絕回答記者提問，獲警員護送至特別通道離開。<br />\n<br />\n在場記者起哄，指昨日已有兩名男子疑似假冒記者及偷拍，促警方解釋為何可疑人士能混入記者會。女子於約10分鐘後從特別通道步出現身解釋，惟只強調「大家都喺度影相，我哋都喺度影相，我都係記者嚟㗎，就係咁簡單」，又指自己已把名片交予警員跟進，「你哋有咩資格查我身份呢？」<br />\n<br />\n該女子的卡片上的名稱為陳曉前，職銜為廣東廣播電視台融媒發展部總監。警察公共關係科首席新聞主任（傳媒）蘇美儀及後解釋，警方會盡量便利傳媒的採訪權，「有時（你哋）冇帶記者證，有時係實習記者」，指該女子的名片與身份證明文件相符，稍後將會就記者會上該出示記者證或記者名片的問題作討論。最後女子於警員護送下離開記者室。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w274/public/column_images/08206.jpg?itok=HtFul78D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw274%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F08206.jpg%3Fitok%3DHtFul78D&h=c1fd2d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGKnOCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGKnOCv.png&h=7238817f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pL1tKaT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpL1tKaT.png&h=d822e845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBDcrri.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBDcrri.png&h=068352b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iDmhCx0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDmhCx0.png&h=904da31a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gSHOEH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gSHOEH.png&h=e58e8929&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Hh1jMo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Hh1jMo.png&h=c7b1980d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9268919a27d33b03d1419198595993f94eb6dc47","tid":1492872,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1b4a72188a95d68ffb608cea0fa82ca5e11cc7","tid":1492872,"uid":84044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:19:56.000Z","msg":"記者嘅哥哥姐姐<br />\n希望你哋好似上次咁帶晒gear入場保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c896e76a0927e344fb6f94eb76d55a53cf9c6c41","tid":1492872,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"其實要associate with<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共+港共縱容嘅hate speech</strong></span><br />\n根本係鼓動啲so called愛國愛港嘅人嚟斬反送中嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>hate speech+fake news先係暴力源頭</strong></span><br />\n何君妖之流，警察員佐級協會阿頭之流<br />\n唔駛協助調查唔駛譴責？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好當將軍澳係單一事件<br />\n中共最叻挑起民族情緒<br />\n人民打斬人民</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n加上警方，政府縱容<br />\n打斬反送中嘅就唔拉/hea拉<br />\n咁就做成咗 原來斬人打人無事<br />\n<br />\n咁=縱容暴力<br />\n唔能夠次次記招都比佢哋話唔評論個別個案/元朗,荃灣.北角斬人都重視"},{"pid":"e75d272e3ed88506efc20bce202ea4157a6a6c26","tid":1492872,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"卡片係人都印得,屌你老母"},{"pid":"1fe09d70c842785ef4cc2e542f59dbdf71a7002d","tid":1492872,"uid":209704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"今日元朗 明日香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SSuK2ya.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSSuK2ya.jpg&h=df53eec0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzWYnyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzWYnyb.jpg&h=598017e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSbQX6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h